### A.3 System Angular Momentum â€” Full Derivation

The total angular momentum of the four-body system in ğ’©:

**H_sys = Î£â‚™â‚Œâ‚€Â³ Hâ‚™ + H_ctrl**

where H_ctrl is the stored angular momentum in the AAMCS actuators (CMGs or reaction wheels used for fine control). The constraint of zero net external torque (free-flying station in orbit) imposes:

**dH_sys/dt = Ï„_ext â‰ˆ Ï„_dist**

